                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On March 17 <persName corresp="#p_CGLD1">Clay</persName> held a top secret
                    teletype conference with <persName corresp="#p_VTS1">Voorhees</persName>
                    concerning the general trend of events in Germany and the negotiation <pb
                        facs="0610" n="573" xml:id="pg_573"/> in London on prohibited and restricted
                    industries. For the transcript of this conference, see <ref target="#pg_105"
                        >page 105</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
